   153→Force a retry from an `afterResponse` hook.
   154→
   155→This allows you to retry a request based on the response content, even if the response has a successful status code. The retry will respect the `retry.limit` option and skip the `shouldRetry` check. The forced retry is observable in `beforeRetry` hooks, where the error will be a `ForceRetryError`.
